* Optimise device-specific web experiences, including mobile phones, tablets and desktop devices;
* Work on new initiatives to help us communicate and help our users to find, book and manage their bookings directly from Vio.com;
* Identify opportunities for improvements in terms of code quality, automation tests, feature and overall product quality.


**Who you are**


* You have proven experience (3+ years) working in full stack development using modern front-end and back-end toolsets and frameworks - we don't require experience with any specific framework, but we do expect experience with a modern set up and tooling environment. Experience with a back-end technology such as Python, NodeJS or Go will help you cross bridges in achieving your goals autonomously;
